---
title: Sheet Pan Crunchy Chicken with Ranch Crema plus Roasted Potatoes & Herby Broccoli
description: Everything in this winner-winner chicken dinner is roasted on one baking sheet: juicy seasoned chicken cutlets coated in light, crispy panko breadcrumbs, ranch-spiced broccoli, and spiced potato wedges. Drizzle that crispy chicken with a quick homemade ranch crema, then dig right in (and enjoy very little digging out to do—what a perfect weeknight meal!).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65b96c88ad32b3177ec44f4b-06a0cd76.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/65b96c88ad32b3177ec44f4b.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: North America
